Any outdoor area used by chickens or bantams shall be fenced so as
to prohibit harm to the chickens or bantams and so as to limit the
chickens or bantams to within the fenced area;

Private tennis courts are permitted subject to the
following requirements:[Added 9-10-1979 by L.L. No. 2-1979;
amended 5-3-1982 by L.L. No. 6-1982; 8-4-1986 by L.L. No. 7-1986; 7-5-1989 by L.L. No. 4-1989]

Any
grant of relief shall not cause or allow any adverse environmental
effect;
